title: [1508521049] Ramsay Meets The Prisoners | Gordon Behind Bars
description:
Gordon takes on one of his toughest challenges when he tries to whip a crew of prison misfits into a fully functional kitchen brigade. While introducing himself, some of the prisoners get a little cheeky. From 'Gordon Behind Bars'.
